<template>
    <q-dialog persistent>
        <q-card style="width: 400px;height: 400px;">
            
            <q-card-section>
                {{ data }}
            </q-card-section>
            <q-card-actions align="right">
                <q-btn flat label="OK" color="primary" v-close-popup />
            </q-card-actions>
        </q-card>
    </q-dialog>
</template>

<script setup>
import { defineComponent} from 'vue';

defineComponent({
    name: 'DialogDetalhesCliente',
    props: {
        data: {
            type: Object,
            required: true
        }
    }
});
</script>
